  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to quantify the degree of sleep disturbances after hip or knee
      replacement surgery.

      Through polysomnographic monitoring the disturbances in sleep stages will be clarified.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
